data.content: #Crew8 Update: After an overnight stay at Ascension Sacred Heart Pensacola in Florida, our NASA astronaut was released and returned to NASAs Johnson Space Center in Houston today. The crew member is in good health and will resume normal post-flight reconditioning with other crew
